<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.2.3">
<l>takkār mikkār kaḷaiccañca lañceyyuñ calavarai</l>
<l>tekkā neṟiyēpōk kuvikkuñ celvaṉ poṉmalai</l>
<l>yekkāla muñceṉṟu cēvit tirukku maṭiyarai</l>
<l>yakkā ṉeṟiyaimāṟṟun taṇtiru māliruñ cōlaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The golden mountain of the wealthy Lord</l>
<l rend="indent">who sent on the path to hell the ferocious [demons]</l>
<l rend="indent">who caused [both] virtuous and the excellent men grief,</l>
<l>is cool Tirumāliruñcōlai where that wilderness path</l>
<l rend="indent">is transformed for devotees who</l>
<l rend="indent">are always going and serving [the Lord].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
